</emphasis>
, female. A, habitus, right; B, urosome, ventral; C, left caudal ramus, dorsal; D, rostrum; E, antennule; F, antenna; G, labrum; H, mandible; I, paragnath; J, maxillule. Scale bars: A, 0.5 mm; B, 0.2 mm; C–F, H, 0.1 mm; G, I, J, 0.05 mm.
